def matrix_determinant(matrix):
    """
    Calculates the determinant of a matrix.
    """
    if len(matrix) == 1:
        return matrix[0][0]
    else:
        return matrix[0][0] * matrix[-1][-1] - matrix[-1][0] * matrix[0][-1]
